cp\u003eOf course, there are a number of switches out there with more features, but for something simple and easy to use, we think this one from TP-Link is going to be a good option. Just make sure to grab it while it\u0026#39;s still on sale for $10.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n                            \n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
